@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component TCK {
  + emits tick
}

component FSM {
  + step()
  + evaluate guards
  + route intent
}

component Component {
  + owns registers
  + performs work
}

database BLS {
  + belief ledger
  + read-only to FSM
}

TCK --> FSM : tick
FSM --> BLS : read beliefs
FSM --> BLS : _commit
FSM --> Component : _send
FSM --> TCK : _tck (enable/disable/rate)

Component --> BLS : commit beliefs
@enduml
